Package org.jpedal.examples.viewer.gui.generic

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GUIButton
    abstract button object into interface
    GUIButtons
    Abstract class so we can use getButtons and instantiate JavaFXButtons.java and Buttons.java objects in either SwingGUI.java or JavaFXGUI.java which ensures Swing code(Buttons.java) stays in SwingGUI.java and JavaFX code(JavaFXButtons.java) stays in JavaFXGUI, keeping GUI.java generic.
    GUICombo
    abstract version of ComboBox
    GUILayersPanel  
    GUIMouseHandler
    abstract level of mouse support in Viewer
    GUIOutline
    abstract level for outlines panel
    GUISearchList  
    GUISearchWindow
    abstract level of search window
    GUIThumbnailPanel
    generic version to show thumbnails in panel on side
